      • findInDataContext

        @Nullable
T findInDataContext(com.intellij.openapi.actionSystem.DataContext context)
        This is a start point for almost all diagrams. An implementation should try to find an element of type T which will be used for data model creation.
        Parameters:
        context - data context
        Returns:
        null if diagram can't be shown or an element of type T to create data model based on it
